These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
Nationality: chinese, indian
Job: bartender, writer
Sport: cycling, surfing
Hobby: singing, fishing
1. Hobby:fishing is on the left or right of Sport:surfing##3
2. Nationality:indian is in an even position##4
3. Job:writer == Nationality:chinese##1
4. Hobby:fishing is on the right of Hobby:singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Nationality      | chinese  | indian   |
| Job   | writer     | bartender   |
| Sport         | surfing | cycling |
| Hobby     | singing | fishing    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
Color: purple, red
House: ranch-style, victorian
Sport: skiing, baseball
Transport: motorbike, tram
1. Sport:baseball is in an odd position##4
2. House:ranch-style == Transport:tram##1
3. Color:red is on the right of House:victorian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Color          | purple     | red |
| House   | victorian | ranch-style  |
| Sport           | baseball         | skiing     |
| Transport     | motorbike   | tram    |

