.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-6::.
Flower: balloon-flower, bellflower
Nationality: dutch, egyptian
City: nizza, edinburgh
Birthday: april, november
1. Birthday:november is in an even position##4
2. Nationality:egyptian is on the far left or far right##3
3. Flower:bellflower == Nationality:dutch##1
4. City:nizza is on the left of Nationality:egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Flower           | bellflower | balloon-flower    |
| Nationality   | dutch       | egyptian |
| City           | nizza         | edinburgh    |
| Birthday         | april    | november   |

